extensionMeta.name: Sheet Navigation & Actions
extensionMeta.description: Sense Sheet Navigation + Actions visualization extension for Qlik Sense.
extensionMeta.author: Stefan Walther

qFieldDefs: =if (Num(Date([Customer Source Date])) > Num(Date([Customer First Invoicing Date])) ,  'Wrong Date' , 'Correct Date')

qDef.qDef:
Pick
(
	$(v_Switch_Option_CM_YTD_CustomerSource)
    ,Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
    ,Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
    ,Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year =  , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice MT])
)

Pick
(
	$(v_Switch_Option_CM_YTD_CustomerSource)
    ,Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])/1000
    ,Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = {$(v_Max_Year)} , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])/1000
     ,Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year =  , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])/1000
)

Pick
(
	$(v_Switch_Option_CM_YTD_CustomerSource)
    ,
            (
              Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
              -Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {$(v_Max_Month_ID)}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice Cost USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
            )
        /1000
    ,$(v_Sales_Contribution_Amount_YTD)/1000
    ,
            (
              Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice Amount USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
              -Sum({$<[Sales Type] = {'Net Sales'}, [Currency Sorting Key]={$(=MaxString([Currency Sorting Key]))},[Month ID] = {"<=$(v_Max_Month_ID)"}, Year = , Quarter=, Month=, [Month Year]=>} [Invoice Cost USD]*[Currency Average Rate])
            )
        /1000
)
